sentences.english: Melon's skin is thin, only about one-third of thick watermelon rind.
sentences.chinese: 哈密瓜的皮很薄，大约只有西瓜皮的三分之一厚。

sentences.english: Plain of two-thirds of the total.
sentences.chinese: 平原占总面积的三分之二。

sentences.english: Today one-third of the people on Greenland earn their living in the fishing industry.
sentences.chinese: 今天格陵兰岛上有三分之一的人在捕鱼业中谋生。

sentences.english: They docked a third of his wages.
sentences.chinese: 他们扣掉他三分之一工资。

sentences.english: I took three consecutive shots from beyond the three-point line and made all three-perfectly.
sentences.chinese: 我连续三次在三分线外远投，三个都进得很漂亮。

sentences.english: Two thirds of the students in our class are League members.
sentences.chinese: 我们班上三分之二的学生是共青团员。

sentences.english: The fair and impartial evaluation, also penetrating the.
sentences.chinese: 这些评价非常中肯，也都入木三分的。

sentences.english: He's trying to make a three-point shot.
sentences.chinese: 他正试著要投一个三分球。

sentences.english: About one-third had previously been sexually active.
sentences.chinese: 其中大概有三分之一的人在此之前有过性活跃状态。

sentences.english: The book, which he borrowed from me yesterday, cost 1/3 of my salary.
sentences.chinese: 他昨天从我这儿借走的那本书花了我三分之一的工资。

sentences.english: At his death, he had lost about a third of his weight and had only a few dollars.
sentences.chinese: 他死时，体重锐减约三分之一，而且身上只剩几文钱。

sentences.english: More than one-third of exploratory wells came up dry.
sentences.chinese: 三分之一强的探勘井都是干井。

sentences.english: Ray just broke Reggie's NBA 3-point record this season.
sentences.chinese: 雷阿伦在该赛季刚刚打破了雷吉米勒的三分球记录。

sentences.english: Over one third of all child deaths are linked to malnutrition.
sentences.chinese: 所有儿童死亡中三分之一以上与营养不良有关。

sentences.english: Presidents have invariably also been Protestants and two-thirds of them have been college graduates.
sentences.chinese: 总统千篇一律是新教徒，而且三分之二是大学毕业生。

sentences.english: One thirds of the water is dirty.
